222
00:10:11,160 --> 00:10:12,930
Dôjdem pre pivo.

223
00:10:12,930 --> 00:10:14,060
Poďme spolu.

224
00:10:31,550 --> 00:10:32,930
Pohryzol ma komár.

225
00:10:36,220 --> 00:10:37,020
Sung Soo, plačeš?

226
00:10:39,490 --> 00:10:42,530
