275
00:13:19,060 --> 00:13:20,270
Pripravený.

276
00:13:20,270 --> 00:13:21,180
Akcia.

277
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,100
Poďme sa vziať.

278
00:13:27,550 --> 00:13:29,090
Možno nemám nič.

279
