00:35:04,100 --> 00:35:06,240
Dala si mi tieto drahé hodinky, 
pretože si vďačná?

654
00:35:06,650 --> 00:35:07,900
Je to darček na rozlúčku?

655
00:35:09,450 --> 00:35:10,370
Hyun Joo.

656
00:35:11,130 --> 00:35:15,050
V tú noc to bolo pre teba poprvýkrát, nie?

